@startuml
state Initial
state GoodsAdded
state PriceUpdated
state GoodsRemoved
state OrderPlaced
state InvoiceGenerated
state ItemSelected
state DiscountAndTaxCalculated
state ReceiptGenerated
state RequestRecorded
state SummaryReportGenerated

Initial --> GoodsAdded : add goods
Initial --> PriceUpdated : update price
Initial --> GoodsRemoved : remove goods
GoodsExpired --> GoodsRemoved : notify removal
Initial --> OrderPlaced : place order
OrderPlaced --> InvoiceGenerated : generate invoice
Initial --> ItemSelected : search and select item
ItemSelected --> DiscountAndTaxCalculated : calculate discount and tax
DiscountAndTaxCalculated --> ReceiptGenerated : generate receipt
ReceiptCancelledOrReplaced --> Initial : cancel/replace receipt
Initial --> RequestRecorded : record request for unavailable item
RequestRecorded --> Initial : process request later
Initial --> SummaryReportGenerated : view transactions

note right of GoodsExpired
Goods are automatically removed after expiration
end note
@enduml
